## Summary
- Add `/wallets` download hub with Qt checksum fallbacks (v1.2.2.0 when v1.3.0.0 Qt assets missing) and network bootstrap snippets
- New APIs: `wallet-hub`, `network-dashboard`, `recent-transactions`, `rental-overview`, `spork-gates`, `network-peers`
- Lazy-load profile/shop wallet tabs; explorer and hosting pages show live network, rental, and tx data
- Wire unused C++ sporks + ops sporks 112–115; expand seeds/peers and fix default wallet config generation
- Deploy manifest updated for wallet/network assets

